# No Co-author Attribution

- Do not add "Co-authored by" or "Co-authored-by: Cursor" (or similar) to commit messages.
- Do not add co-author footers or attribution lines to README, docs, or any generated content.
- Keep commits and project content attribution-free unless the user explicitly asks otherwise.
